    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.2",
          "pli": "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, form is impermanent. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.3",
          "pli": "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ; ",
          "en": "What’s impermanent is suffering. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.4",
          "pli": "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā; ",
          "en": "What’s suffering is not-self. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.5",
          "pli": "yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. ",
          "en": "And what’s not-self should be truly seen with right understanding like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.6",
          "pli": "Vedanā … ",
          "en": "Feeling … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.7",
          "pli": "saññā … ",
          "en": "Perception … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.8",
          "pli": "saṅkhārā … ",
          "en": "Choices … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.9",
          "pli": "viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ. ",
          "en": "Consciousness is impermanent. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.10",
          "pli": "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ; ",
          "en": "What’s impermanent is suffering. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.11",
          "pli": "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā; ",
          "en": "What’s suffering is not-self. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:1.12",
          "pli": "yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. ",
          "en": "And what’s not-self should be truly seen with right understanding like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:2.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati, vedanāyapi … saññāyapi … saṅkhāresupi … viññāṇasmimpi nibbindati. ",
          "en": "Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:2.2",
          "pli": "Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. ",
          "en": "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:2.3",
          "pli": "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānāti. ",
          "en": "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’ "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:2.4",
          "pli": "Yāvatā, bhikkhave, sattāvāsā, yāvatā bhavaggaṃ, ete aggā, ete seṭṭhā lokasmiṃ yadidaṃ arahanto”ti. ",
          "en": "As far as there are abodes of sentient beings, even up until the pinnacle of existence, the perfected ones are the foremost and the best.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:3.1",
          "pli": "Idamavoca bhagavā. ",
          "en": "That is what the Buddha said. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:3.2",
          "pli": "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: ",
          "en": "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:4.1",
          "pli": "“Sukhino vata arahanto, ",
          "en": "“Oh! How happy are the perfected ones! "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:4.2",
          "pli": "taṇhā tesaṃ na vijjati; ",
          "en": "Craving is not found in them, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:4.3",
          "pli": "Asmimāno samucchinno, ",
          "en": "the conceit ‘I am’ is cut off, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:4.4",
          "pli": "mohajālaṃ padālitaṃ. ",
          "en": "and the net of delusion is shattered. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:5.1",
          "pli": "Anejaṃ te anuppattā, ",
          "en": "They’ve attained imperturbability, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:5.2",
          "pli": "cittaṃ tesaṃ anāvilaṃ; ",
          "en": "their minds are unclouded, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:5.3",
          "pli": "Loke anupalittā te, ",
          "en": "nothing in the world clings to them, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:5.4",
          "pli": "brahmabhūtā anāsavā. ",
          "en": "they’ve become holy, undefiled. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:6.1",
          "pli": "Pañcakkhandhe pariññāya, ",
          "en": "Completely understanding the five aggregates, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:6.2",
          "pli": "satta saddhammagocarā; ",
          "en": "their domain is the seven good qualities. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:6.3",
          "pli": "Pasaṃsiyā sappurisā, ",
          "en": "Those good people are praiseworthy, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:6.4",
          "pli": "puttā buddhassa orasā. ",
          "en": "the Buddha’s rightful children. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:7.1",
          "pli": "Sattaratanasampannā, ",
          "en": "Endowed with the seven gems, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:7.2",
          "pli": "Tīsu sikkhāsu sikkhitā; ",
          "en": "and trained in the three trainings, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:7.3",
          "pli": "Anuvicaranti mahāvīrā, ",
          "en": "the great heroes live on, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:7.4",
          "pli": "Pahīnabhayabheravā. ",
          "en": "with fear and dread given up. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:8.1",
          "pli": "Dasahaṅgehi sampannā, ",
          "en": "Endowed with ten factors, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:8.2",
          "pli": "mahānāgā samāhitā; ",
          "en": "those giants have immersion. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:8.3",
          "pli": "Ete kho seṭṭhā lokasmiṃ, ",
          "en": "These are the best in the world, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:8.4",
          "pli": "taṇhā tesaṃ na vijjati. ",
          "en": "craving is not found in them. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:9.1",
          "pli": "Asekhañāṇamuppannaṃ, ",
          "en": "The master’s knowledge has arisen: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:9.2",
          "pli": "antimoyaṃ samussayo; ",
          "en": "‘This bag of bones is my last.’ "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:9.3",
          "pli": "Yo sāro brahmacariyassa, ",
          "en": "They are independent of others "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:9.4",
          "pli": "tasmiṃ aparapaccayā. ",
          "en": "in the core of the spiritual path. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:10.1",
          "pli": "Vidhāsu na vikampanti, ",
          "en": "Unwavering in the face of discrimination, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:10.2",
          "pli": "vippamuttā punabbhavā; ",
          "en": "they’re freed from future lives. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:10.3",
          "pli": "Dantabhūmimanuppattā, ",
          "en": "They’ve reached the level of the tamed, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:10.4",
          "pli": "te loke vijitāvino. ",
          "en": "in the world, they’re the winners. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:11.1",
          "pli": "Uddhaṃ tiriyaṃ apācīnaṃ, ",
          "en": "Above, below, and all around, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:11.2",
          "pli": "nandī tesaṃ na vijjati; ",
          "en": "relishing is not found in them. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:11.3",
          "pli": "Nadanti te sīhanādaṃ, ",
          "en": "They roar their lion’s roar: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:11.4",
          "pli": "buddhā loke anuttarā”ti. ",
          "en": "‘The awakened are supreme in the world!’” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn22.76:11.5",
          "pli": "Catutthaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
